description: Ranplan Group AB engages in the development and commercialization of software tools. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm. The company went IPO on 2018-06-28. The business activities comprise development of wireless network planning technologies that imply in-building and dense urban outdoor planning tool for wireless fidelity (WiFi), fourth generation (4G) or Long-Term Evolution (LTE), 5G mobile networks. Additionally, the Company offers multiple technology standards supporting Public Safety wireless, Industrial Internet of Things and Smart City applications. The firm operates worldwide through its subsidiaries.
naicsNationalIndustry: Radio and Television Broadcasting and Wireless Communications Equipment Manufacturing
